responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "BBAB1E6F42693B5F20162F8084D172FB", "It must be those goblins riling the spirits at the Shrine. Thank you for your diligence in putting some of them back to rest before you left that spot. No doubt I\'ll have work to do myself anon. Good work, friend.")
